    "description": "OUR maintained mapping from surface text (en/pt-BR) to a subset of RelAIEO concept IDs. RelAIEO itself has no lexicalizations (it is a formal, reflective auditing ontology); this layer is how the guardrail activates ontology concepts from a prompt/response. It references only concept IDs that exist in relaieo.ttl. Keeping it separate leaves the upstream ontology pristine.",
    "created": "2026-07-01",
    "grounds_concept_ids_from": "ontologies/relaieo.ttl"
  },
